OOC:(  OK, heres part of what happened. As far as I'm aware of.
If I get anything mixed up, please correct me.

Quickstrike was rescued and placed in a CR chamber.  The mind reading 
horse Wildfire read his mind and was able to restore most of 
Quickstrike back to normal.  Stringtra is currently watching over 
Quickstrike who is in his quarters resting.

DarkMouse was found and her memory restored.  She is back in the Pred 
base.

The rescue attemp by Prowl is still under way.  They rescued her but 
they are under attack while fleeing the Alliance base. 

Spears and Striker are over the ocean in a por returning back to the 
Ark.

Ramulus is on North America, at Spears' pod to get parts for from it 
for repaairs for the Ark.

Battera and Rex are talking on the Cybertron fire.

Lunarpine is off hunting something.

I'm not sure where Rowdy Wolf is.

The Alliance and Megatron are working on a deal.

Megatron is trying to come up with a plan to take over all the 
Predacons on earth.

Vulois is making arrangements to have all the group leaders meet and 
have a treaty conference.
